{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I always wanted to play an action game where I could take direct control of a capital ship in 3D space. Not fake 3D where you're on the same plane, actual 6-Axis Freedom of Movement. One day, I decided to make that game. As a solo developer, I poured two years into crafting <i>Galactic Warship,</i> letting you pilot massive capital-class warships in full 3D with complete 6-axis freedom. You'll unlock dozens of ships, each armed with powerful, customizable weapons, as you face waves of enemies and insane bosses from outside our reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Full Command of Capital-Class Warships:</strong> Finally, a game that puts the full weight of commanding these massive ships in your hands. Navigate, dodge, and engage in epic battles, with the freedom to move on all six axes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Growing Arsenal to Match the Threat:</strong> As you progress, you\u2019ll gain access to an ever-expanding array of ships and weapons to suit your style. Progression is constant, every sector you complete unlocks a permanent upgrade that will help you on your next run.\u00a0\u00a0<br>\u00a0 \u00a0<br><strong>Infinite Replayability:</strong> No two runs will be the same, and I will be adding new missions, ships, and features with the help of player feedback.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737149233","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515950/page.bg.jpg?t=1737149233","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515950/67ff076e693518c51dcf2f347c343319489cc419/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737149233","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515950/67ff076e693518c51dcf2f347c343319489cc419/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737149233","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"conte